Package oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.socialnetwork.model.pojo

Interface Summary
ViewObjectStructureVisitor Definition of the visitor to be used in a Visitor pattern that can be applied to Social Network Nodes.
XmlOsnParsableNode Signifies that the implementer is a node belonging to the Oracle Social Network XML file.
 

Class Summary
FndOsnIntegrationNode Used for reading in the fnd-osn-integration xml node from the fnd-osn-integration.xml OSN metadata file.
OsnRootNode The very top root node that all other loaded Social Network objects will reside within.
SocialNetworkStructureStorage A container that stores the collections of the node structures so that they can be referenced by multiple node usages.
SocialNetworkTreeDataCollector Temporary object used during tree creation to consolidate the additional pieces of information that are needed whilst the tree is being created.
